polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源：<a href="https://www.nathanielbullard.com/presentations">纳特·布拉德</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>中国是迄今为止最严重的罪犯，无视自己的气候承诺， <a href="https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/chinas-coal-country-full-steam-ahead-with-new-power-plants-despite-climate-2023-11-30/">开设了大量新的燃煤电厂</a>。发达民主国家根本没有建设新的燃煤电厂，而除中国以外的发展中国家现在建设的也很少： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc56dd01f-0b1a-47dc-9b67-a64f627e9d88_940x528.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc56dd01f-0b1a-47dc-9b67-a64f627e9d88_940x528.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc56dd01f-0b1a-47dc-9b67-a64f627e9d88_940x528.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc56dd01f-0b1a-47dc-9b67-a64f627e9d88_940x528.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc56dd01f-0b1a-47dc-9b67-a64f627e9d88_940x528.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc56dd01f-0b1a-47dc-9b67-a64f627e9d88_940x528.jpeg" width="940" height="528" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/c56dd01f-0b1a-47dc-9b67-a64f627e9d88_940x528.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:528,&quot;width&quot;:940,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:34542,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" title="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc56dd01f-0b1a-47dc-9b67-a64f627e9d88_940x528.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc56dd01f-0b1a-47dc-9b67-a64f627e9d88_940x528.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc56dd01f-0b1a-47dc-9b67-a64f627e9d88_940x528.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc56dd01f-0b1a-47dc-9b67-a64f627e9d88_940x528.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源：<a href="https://www.nathanielbullard.com/presentations">纳特·布拉德</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>当然，中国也是全球绿色能源，特别是太阳能电池板和电池的主要建设者。那挺好的。但只要中国继续大量燃烧煤炭——这与其自身的<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/china-must-stop-its-coal-industry">政治激励</a>和产业政策有关——气候变化就会继续恶化。显然，美国和欧洲应该继续减少煤炭和石油的使用。但如果没有中国（和东南亚）的参与，西方的努力可能会被抵消。</p><p>当你提到这个事实时，左撇子气候活动人士会非常生气，但这是事实。目前还不清楚发达国家可以采取哪些措施来影响中国的行为。不过， <a href="https://insideclimatenews.org/news/03102023/todays-climate-european-union-worlds-first-carbon-tariff-united-states/">碳关税</a>将是一个好的开始。还有其他想法，例如从印度尼西亚等出口国购买煤炭并将其埋在地下，这样中国就无法燃烧它。无论如何，这是一个更长的帖子的主题。</p><h4>绿色能源是实实在在的</h4><p>我们战胜气候变化的最大希望——也是近年来情况<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/our-climate-change-debates-are-out">如此光明的</a>原因——是<em>技术</em>。太阳能和电池存储处于陡峭的学习曲线上，这意味着我们部署的越多，成本就越低。电池尤为重要，因为它们有两个主要用途：替代石油作为交通（电动汽车）的动力来源，并通过消除间歇性帮助太阳能和风能取代煤炭。</p><p>让我们从太阳能和风能开始。目前，由于中国的大量生产，太阳能电池板<a href="https://cleantechnica.com/2023/12/26/solar-panel-prices-down-30-40-in-2023-us-prices-down-15">非常便宜，几乎是免费的</a>。土地和安装成本 <a href="https://www.freeingenergy.com/facts/solar-commercial-residential-utility-cost-watt-g113/">也在下降</a>，尽管速度较慢。风能也变得越来越便宜，尽管速度较慢，而且土地成本也更高。</p><p>但无论如何，由于太阳能和风能现在非常便宜，公用事业公司开始大量安装它们。截至 2022 年，太阳能和风能几乎占全球发电量的八分之一，2023 年将再次出现大幅增长： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe9b272ed-ee00-4603-831b-aba161227ed8_938x528.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe9b272ed-ee00-4603-831b-aba161227ed8_938x528.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fs