一些重大障碍——中国煤炭工业、中东的挥霍、美国的邻避主义等等。但与 15 年前形成鲜明对比的是，我们现在拥有完成工作的工具。 </p><div><hr></div><p class="button-wrapper" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.noahpinion.blog/subscribe?&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Subscribe now&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}" data-component-name="ButtonCreateButton"><a class="button primary" href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/subscribe?"><span>现在订阅</span></a></p><p class="button-wrapper" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/a-bunch-of-handy-charts-about-climate?utm_source=substack&utm_medium=email&utm_content=share&action=share&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Share&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}" data-component-name="ButtonCreateButton"> <a class="button primary" href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/a-bunch-of-handy-charts-about-climate?utm_source=substack&utm_medium=email&utm_content=share&action=share"><span>分享</span></a></p>; 
2024 could be the pivotal year for Cold War 2China's economy has weakened, but the U.S. may be taken off the board. https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/2024-could-be-the-pivotal-year-for https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/2024-could-be-the-pivotal-year-forNoah Smith Mon, 12 Feb 2024 11:26:48 GMT <div class="captioned-image-container"><figure> <a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa1831969-488e-4875-a4cd-8e4c99946edb_955x506.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa1831969-488e-4875-a4cd-8e4c99946edb_955x506.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa1831969-488e-4875-a4cd-8e4c99946edb_955x506.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa1831969-488e-4875-a4cd-8e4c99946edb_955x506.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa1831969-488e-4875-a4cd-8e4c99946edb_955x506.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa1831969-488e-4875-a4cd-8e4c99946edb_955x506.jpeg" width="955" height="506" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/a1831969-488e-4875-a4cd-8e4c99946edb_955x506.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:506,&quot;width&quot;:955,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:36306,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa1831969-488e-4875-a4cd-8e4c99946edb_955x506.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa1831969-488e-4875-a4cd-8e4c99946edb_955x506.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa1831969-488e-4875-a4cd-8e4c99946edb_955x506.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa1831969-488e-4875-a4cd-8e4c99946edb_955x506.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" fetchpriority="high"></picture></div></a> <polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></figure></div><p>当我写关于世界事务的文章时，我倾向于使用一些术语，比如“<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/the-war-economy-sizing-up-the-new">新轴心</a>”和“<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/a-lot-of-what-you-see-in-the-news">冷战2</a> ”，这可能看起来很夸张。但我使用这些术语的目的并不是为了激怒或吓唬人们；而是为了让他们感到高兴。这是因为我认为它们有效地描述了当今世界正在发生的事情。 《冷战 2》只是<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/a-lot-of-what-you-see-in-the-news">一个思维模型，</a>用于思考地缘政治叙事、效忠和组织如何在两个敌对集团之间分裂。我将中国、俄罗斯和伊朗称为“新轴心国”，因为它们的伙伴关系更多的是针对美国的松散、方便的结盟，而不是紧密、合作的联盟——类似于德国、日本和意大利作为方便伙伴的方式在第二次世界大战中。</p><p>无论如何，我认为 2024 年将成为《冷战 2》的关键一年。</p><p> 2022 年对于新轴心来说是灾难性的一年。普京征服乌克兰的企图出人意料地遭到挫败，暴露了俄罗斯军事机器的许多弱点，并使西方武器装备相形见绌。这场战争促使台湾开始更加认真地对待自己的防御，并吓得中国至少暂时试图与俄罗斯保持距离。与此同时，中期选举<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/why-the-midterms-make-me-optimistic">让美国看​​起来更加稳定</a>。</p><p> 2023年，帝国发起反击。尽管德国人和英国人犹豫不决，但俄罗斯动员了整个社会参加战争。 <a href="https://www.washingtonpost.com/opinions/2023/12/07/ukraine-counteroffensive-russia-war-drones-stalemate/">事实证明，西方武器不足以</a>让乌克兰人在俄罗斯坚决的防御面前前进。由于塔克·卡尔森孜孜不倦的反乌克兰宣传和埃隆·马斯克的转变，反对乌克兰援助成为美国右翼的主导立场。十月份，新轴心国获得了一笔巨大的意外之财——加沙战争将美国的注意力和资源从亚洲和欧洲转移开，尽管它分裂了进步运动。</p><p>但与此同时，一个重大事件从长远来看有可能削弱新轴心国的权力：中国的<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/why-chinas-economy-ran-off-the-rails">房地产崩溃</a>加速，有效地结束了三十年来决定该国世界地位的快速经济增长。</p><p>现在已经是 2024 年了。所有迹象都表明今年是全球竞争的关键一年。一方面，中国经济的疲软使新轴心国的对手威胁性减弱，但这种转变非常缓慢且微不足道。另一方面，美国国内的政治动荡有可能将其排除在外，从而使中国在亚洲可以放手一搏。与此同时，加沙战争不断恶化，转移了美国对亚洲<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/asia-is-much-more-important-to-us">更为重要的战场的</a>注意力和资源。</p><h4>中国经济疲软是新轴心力量的核心</h4><p>美国在第二次世界大战中通过<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Military_production_during_World_War_II">生产超过对手而压倒了他们</a>。冷战时期，美国及其发达民主盟国在军备竞赛中击败了苏联，并通过对半导体工业的掌握在精密武器领域<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Offset_strategy#Second_Offset_Strategy">取得了优势</a>。但在第二次冷战中，推动自由国家在 20 世纪取得胜利的经济主导地位<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/people-are-realizing-that-the-arsenal">已不复存在</a>。中国向世界工厂的转变平衡了专制国家和民主国家之间的经济实力平衡： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4334a30a-c968-41cc-a819-38236706b47a_797x574.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4334a30a-c968-41c