to,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F05c33c13-2a4f-42fc-ae14-75da9fcf3559_1020x720.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F05c33c13-2a4f-42fc-ae14-75da9fcf3559_1020x720.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F05c33c13-2a4f-42fc-ae14-75da9fcf3559_1020x720.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F05c33c13-2a4f-42fc-ae14-75da9fcf3559_1020x720.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>这就是使美国在过去几十年中保持<a href="https://seekingalpha.com/article/308958-charting-world-shares-of-gdp">相当恒定的全球GDP份额的</a>原因，即使中国和东南亚的部分地区和东欧赶上了。</p><p>部分原因是美国生活水平的提高更快： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0a71203e-22e6-4f4c-8b8f-fb9068ede671_1360x972.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0a71203e-22e6-4f4c-8b8f-fb9068ede671_1360x972.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0a71203e-22e6-4f4c-8b8f-fb9068ede671_1360x972.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0a71203e-22e6-4f4c-8b8f-fb9068ede671_1360x972.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0a71203e-22e6-4f4c-8b8f-fb9068ede671_1360x972.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0a71203e-22e6-4f4c-8b8f-fb9068ede671_1360x972.jpeg" width="1360" height="972" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/0a71203e-22e6-4f4c-8b8f-fb9068ede671_1360x972.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:972,&quot;width&quot;:1360,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:93995,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0a71203e-22e6-4f4c-8b8f-fb9068ede671_1360x972.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0a71203e-22e6-4f4c-8b8f-fb9068ede671_1360x972.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0a71203e-22e6-4f4c-8b8f-fb9068ede671_1360x972.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0a71203e-22e6-4f4c-8b8f-fb9068ede671_1360x972.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>部分原因是，由于移民率高和更强的生育能力，美国的人口增长速度比其他大多数人的人口更快。</p><p>因此，说美国<em>超过</em>了我们民主发展的盟友并不是疯狂的。认为这代表了<em>要庆祝的东西</em>是错误的。</p><p>差异的一部分是由于良性因素引起的。许多欧洲国家的工人<a href="https://data.oecd.org/emp/hours-worked.htm">工作时间少于</a>美国同行的工作时间，通常是政策的；这减少了人均GDP，但实际上它只是劳动和休闲之间的不同选择。同时，您看到的一些<a href="https://twitter.com/quantian1/status/1750569549412327769">比较</a>有市场汇率；看起来像美国优势的某些部分实际上只是美元变得越来越竞争。</p><p>差异的另一部分可能是由于美国经济模式的优势。这很难确定，因为有很多混杂因素。但是在某些情况下，欧洲明显通过监管损害了其经济。例如，GDPR无论对隐私的好处如何，都对公司施加了真正的经济成本。这来自约翰逊（2022）的文献评论：</p><blockquote><p>本文回顾了有关欧盟一般数据保护法规（GDPR）的经济文献……迄今为止，关于GDPR的经济文献很大程度上（尽管并非普遍）对公司造成了损害。这些危害包括公司绩效，创新，竞争，网络和营销。</p></blockquote><p>软件行业的过度监管可能是欧洲与Google，Microsoft，Apple和Amazon不等效的原因，尽管拥有<a href="https://www.zdnet.com/article/europe-has-more-developers-than-the-us-so-why-doesnt-it-have-more-startups-too/">才华横溢</a>的软件工程师和良好的大学。关键的高价值行业失败肯定会降低生产率。</p><p>但是，这些也代表着欧洲做出与美国不同的选择。美国可以使用我们的软件行业允许我们负担的更大的房屋和更好的电器嘲笑欧洲，他们可以以这样的事实嘲笑我们，因为它们更受到现代浏览器饼干的威胁。</p><p>另一方面，在许多情况下，其他富裕国家显然只是以某种深刻的方式偶然发现了。最严重的例子是意大利。早在1990年，美国人和意大利人的生活水平非常相似。仅仅三十年后，美国又有一半。 </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff888678f-492e-431f-926e-fb07cad828a6_1359x967.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff888678f-492e-431f-926e-fb07cad828a6_1359x967.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff888678f-492e-431f-926e-fb07cad828a6_1359x967.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff888678f-492e-431f-926e-fb07cad828a6_1359x967.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff888678f-492e-431f-926e-fb07cad828a6_1359x967.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff888678f-492e-431f-926e-fb07cad828a6_1359x967.jpeg" width="1359" height="967" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/f888678f-492e-431f-926e-fb07cad828a6_1359x967.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:967,&quot;width&quot;:1359,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:65082,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot