9.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F20824136-e701-43b5-a10f-ae1171e18788_1360x969.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F20824136-e701-43b5-a10f-ae1171e18788_1360x969.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F20824136-e701-43b5-a10f-ae1171e18788_1360x969.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F20824136-e701-43b5-a10f-ae1171e18788_1360x969.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F20824136-e701-43b5-a10f-ae1171e18788_1360x969.jpeg" width="1360" height="969" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/20824136-e701-43b5-a10f-ae1171e18788_1360x969.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:969,&quot;width&quot;:1360,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:64998,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F20824136-e701-43b5-a10f-ae1171e18788_1360x969.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F20824136-e701-43b5-a10f-ae1171e18788_1360x969.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F20824136-e701-43b5-a10f-ae1171e18788_1360x969.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F20824136-e701-43b5-a10f-ae1171e18788_1360x969.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>我已经<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/japans-living-standards-are-too-low">写了关于</a><a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/fixing-japans-broken-corporate-culture">为什么会发生这种情况的</a>文章，所以我不会为您带来漫长的重申。基本上，日本有1）严重的衰老，而2）生产力低，源于破碎的企业文化，该文化是基于资历而不是优点促进人们的，并迫使员工做很多非生产性的忙碌工作。</p><p>也可能还有其他因素，例如出口弱点和来自中国竞争的暴露。但是总的来说，<em>这些事情都没有局势</em>。日本正在成为一个肮脏的国家；城市仍然闪闪发光，但是如果您去人们的家，您会发现这些人比美国人差得多，即使他们工作更长的时间。</p><p>英国和德国也有大大落后的风险。自2008年以来，英国每小时工作的产出基本上根本没有增长： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F679baf89-1544-44be-b3ac-90149b450734_908x650.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F679baf89-1544-44be-b3ac-90149b450734_908x650.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F679baf89-1544-44be-b3ac-90149b450734_908x650.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F679baf89-1544-44be-b3ac-90149b450734_908x650.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F679baf89-1544-44be-b3ac-90149b450734_908x650.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F679baf89-1544-44be-b3ac-90149b450734_908x650.jpeg" width="908" height="650" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/679baf89-1544-44be-b3ac-90149b450734_908x650.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:650,&quot;width&quot;:908,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:68329,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F679baf89-1544-44be-b3ac-90149b450734_908x650.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F679baf89-1544-44be-b3ac-90149b450734_908x650.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F679baf89-1544-44be-b3ac-90149b450734_908x650.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F679baf89-1544-44be-b3ac-90149b450734_908x650.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源： <a href="https://cep.lse.ac.uk/pubs/download/special/cepsp41.pdf?_gl=1*1n9t3c8*_ga*MjA0NTEyMTM3OC4xNjk5NDkzNDk3*_ga_LWTEVFESYX*MTcwNzAzMjcxOC4xLjEuMTcwNzAzMjc2NS4xMy4wLjA.">Van Reenen＆Yang（2023）</a></figcaption></figure></div><p> <a href="https://cep.lse.ac.uk/pubs/download/special/cepsp41.pdf?_gl=1*1n9t3c8*_ga*MjA0NTEyMTM3OC4xNjk5NDkzNDk3*_ga_LWTEVFESYX*MTcwNzAzMjcxOC4xLjEuMTcwNzAzMjc2NS4xMy4wLjA.">经济学家</a>在很大程度上<a href="https://www.niesr.ac.uk/blog/why-uk-productivity-low-and-how-can-it-improve">同意</a>，这是英国长期缺乏商业投资的重要原因。这有多种原因 - 一种重型的工业政策，意味着英国与其他国家相比，金融危机更为严重，这是一个尼姆比制度，使建造住房或工厂很难，与其他国家相比，较低的研发支出，当然也很难英国脱欧。</p><p>至于德国，在2010年代，在强劲的出口表现的背后，它做得很好 - 其中一些来自中国的需求，其中一些来自结构性贸易盈余，而南欧不幸的南欧国家无法贬值，因为他们是欧元的一部分。</p><p>但是在过去的几年中，德国工业机器撞到了砖墙。德国的经济<a href="https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/german-economy-contracted-03-2023-stats-office-2024-01-15/">在2023年下降了0.3％</a> ，您可以阅读有关工业公司如何考虑迁出该国的<a href="https://www.politico.eu/article/rust-belt-on-the-rhine-the-deindustrialization-of-germany/">大量</a><a href="https://www.spiegel.de/international/business/wirtschaftsblunder-why-germany-s-economy-is-flailing-and-what-could-help-a-c5047bf2-0c66-4a8a-bf62-e52baaef0acd">故事</a>。每个人都同意，廉价俄罗斯天然气的截止 - 首先让自己依靠这是<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/germany-needs-to-stop-messing-around">非常愚蠢的</a>- 这是很大的一部分。该国摆脱核电站的<a href="https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2022-04-06/scholz-shoots-down-appeal-to-reverse-germany-s-nuclear-exit">更愚蠢的选择</a>只会加剧了能量紧缩。但是许多<a href="https://www.spiegel.de/international/business/wirtschaftsblunder-why-germany-s-economy-is-flailing-and-what-could-help-a-c5047bf2-0c66-4a8a-bf62-e52baaef0acd">观察家声称</a>，在2010年代的良好年份中，德国使自己变得僵化和过度监管。</p><p>对于美国来说<em>，这绝对不是一个</em>好消息，这是一个贫穷，较弱的德国，英国和意大利，这意味着欧洲将不得不更多地依靠已经过度拉伸的美国来防御俄罗斯威胁。他们将购买更少的美国制造产品，这意味着美国企业的出口收入较少。而且，他们将不太可能协助美国阻止中国在亚洲的侵略。同时，日本是太平洋最坚定的朋友，也是<a href="https://warontherocks.com/2021/11/japans-revolution-on-taiwan-affairs/">我们在台湾任何潜在战争中的主要盟友</a>。日本较弱意味着美国较弱。</p><p>然而，不知何故，许多美国人似乎并没有得到信息。我们<a href="https://twitter.com/DanielDiMartino/status/1752169375375757553">嘲笑“欧洲统一”</a> ，好像民主国家自由的人与美国结盟的人<a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/europeans-poorer-inflation-economy-255eb629">变得越来越贫穷</a>，使我们变得更好。同时，特朗普以关税达到了<a href="https://www.wsj.com/economy/trade/u-s-and-europe-struggle-to-put-trump-era-tariffs-behind-them-e8efead3">欧洲</a>和<a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/u-s-agrees-to-lift-trump-era-tariffs-on-japanese-steel-11644271202">日本</a>。即使拜登政府取消了他们，但疤痕仍然存在。现在，政治过道双方的美国人因日本公司<a href="https://www.atlanticcouncil.org/blogs/new-atlanticist/the-us-steel-deal-is-a-test-of-friendshoring-and-the-us-is-failing/">的收购而在美国钢铁公司的收购中齐心协力</a>，尽管日本是一个友好的国家，尽管日本管理人员<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/why-the-us-steel-industry-is-dying">可能不太可能裁员</a>美国钢铁工人。</p><p>几乎有些美国人通过努力打击任何可以被打击的人来应对我国机构功能障碍的心理影响，而我们相对于中国的衰落 - 即，我们在挣扎中挣扎的盟友比我们遇到的要多得多。 。</p><p>这种态度需要停止。我敦促美国的每个人都记住这张图表： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa8d0a042-ff53-441c-8b1c-794ce77bdef9_797x574.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa8d0a042-ff53-441c-8b1c-794ce77bdef9_797x574.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa8d0a042-ff53-441c-8b1c-794ce77bdef9_797x574.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa8d0a042-ff53-441c-8b1c-794ce77bdef9_797x574.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa8d0a042-ff53-441c-8b1c-794ce77bdef9_797x574.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa8d0a042-ff53-441c-8b1c-794ce77bdef9_797x574.jpeg" width="678" height="488.2961104140527" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/a8d0a042-ff53-441c-8b1c-794ce77bdef9_797x574.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:574,&quot;width&quot;:797,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:678,&quot;bytes&quot;:27404,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa8d0a042-ff53-441c-8b1c-794ce77bdef9_797x574.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa8d0a042-ff53-441c-8b1c-794ce77bdef9_797x574.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa8d0a042-ff53-441c-8b1c-794ce77bdef9_797x574.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa8d0a042-ff53-441c-8b1c-794ce77bdef9_797x574.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源：世界银行</figcaption></figure></div><p>中国的制造业实力如此巨大，以至于只有结合其工业能力，就可以发达的民主国家希望与之相匹配。如果我们继续怀疑和对抗，这将不会发生这种情况。我们需要停止将德国，英国，日本等思考为我们的旧竞争对手，并开始将它们视为我们必不可少的伙伴。他们的力量是我们的力量，他们的弱点是我们的弱点。</p><p>这是我们在第二次世界大战之后和第一场冷战初期意识到的，当时我们制​​定了马歇尔计划，并向欧洲和日本商品开放了市场。我们现在需要记住这种精神。 </p><div><hr></div><p class="button-wrapper" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.noahpinion.blog/subscribe?&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Subscribe now&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}" data-component-