 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd70b50f2-d812-4568-bac1-737ff0568979_802x818.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>这是一个非凡的宏观经济壮举。很少有人认为美联储能够平息大流行通货膨胀而不会丢掉大量的人，但是<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/how-did-the-us-achieve-a-soft-landing">他们以某种方式将其撤下</a>。</p><p>下一个大问题是：美联储今年会降低费率吗？伟大的命运可以坚持这一决定，美国经济的短期命运也是如此。但是答案令人惊讶地不清楚。杰罗姆·鲍威尔（Jerome Powell）最近淡化了三月削减的可能性：</p><blockquote><p>杰罗姆·鲍威尔（Jerome Powell）向中央银行开始削减利率的贸易商发出了明确的信息：不是那么快……鲍威尔（Powell）在3月的下一次会议上强行推动了寄予希望有关通货膨胀始终将通货膨胀率向其目标拉回的更多迹象。</p></blockquote><p>不快速降低利率的明显原因是经济状况良好。标准的宏观经济直觉说，当每个人都有工作并且工资上升时，人们将购买更多东西，这最终将对价格施加上升压力。因此，货币政策的一个基本策略是倾向于强大的经济。</p><p>最重要的是，“如果不破产，请不要修复它”的一般直觉。如果5.33％的利率到目前为止尚未损害实际经济，并且如果他们设法将通货膨胀降低到了目标，那么为什么您会通过回到低利率来摇摆船？</p><p>话虽这么说，我确实认为美联储很可能很快就会开始降低税率，即使不是在三月，然后在三个月后的某个时候。基本上有三个原因使之有意义。首先，从最乐观的角度来看，我们似乎有能力加速生产率的增长。</p><h4>生产力增长看起来正在加速</h4><p><a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/three-reasons-the-federal-reserve">阅读更多</a></p>; 
Biden should run on a message of abundanceThings are going pretty well in America, and Biden's policies have largely helped. https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/biden-should-run-on-a-message-for. https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/biden-should-run-on-a-message-for.Noah Smith Thu, 01 Feb 2024 10:38:56 GMT <div class="captioned-image-container"><figure> <a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7f44cf91-2932-4eb2-8251-ccbd83d779dd_1344x916.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7f44cf91-2932-4eb2-8251-ccbd83d779dd_1344x916.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7f44cf91-2932-4eb2-8251-ccbd83d779dd_1344x916.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7f44cf91-2932-4eb2-8251-ccbd83d779dd_1344x916.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7f44cf91-2932-4eb2-8251-ccbd83d779dd_1344x916.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7f44cf91-2932-4eb2-8251-ccbd83d779dd_1344x916.jpeg" width="716" height="487.98809523809524" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/7f44cf91-2932-4eb2-8251-ccbd83d779dd_1344x916.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:916,&quot;width&quot;:1344,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:716,&quot;bytes&quot;:105751,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7f44cf91-2932-4eb2-8251-ccbd83d779dd_1344x916.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7f44cf91-2932-4eb2-8251-ccbd83d779dd_1344x916.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7f44cf91-2932-4eb2-8251-ccbd83d779dd_1344x916.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7f44cf91-2932-4eb2-8251-ccbd83d779dd_1344x916.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" fetchpriority="high"></picture></div></a> <polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line><figcaption class="image-caption">图片由<a href="https://unsplash.com/@aaronburden?utm_content=creditCopyText&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=unsplash">Aaron Burden</a>在<a href="https://unsplash.com/photos/flag-of-usa-on-grass-field-9C8r4QUwZRQ?utm_content=creditCopyText&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=unsplash">Unsplash</a>上</figcaption></figure></div><p>总统竞选活动正在升温，很快乔·拜登（Joe Biden）将不得不为他的连任辩护。当然，他总是可以回到一个负面信息 -<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/a-vote-for-trump-is-a-vote-for-chaos">唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）是混乱的代理人</a>，而且<a href="https://twitter.com/ArmandDoma/status/1752857671970242636">每天</a>似乎<a href="https://twitter.com/niubi/status/1752727513363579360">都在提醒人们</a><a href="https://twitter.com/GregTSargent/status/1752672012584022493">这一事实</a>。但是，美国人不喜欢投票支持两种邪恶中的小事 - 他们会想听听拜登为何积极好事。</p><p>这可能很棘手；我看过候选人选择错误的消息的情况。最值得注意的是，我记得2000年的阿尔·戈尔（Al Gore）试图向“ <a href="https://slate.com/news-and-politics/2002/08/al-gore-s-bogus-defense-of-his-populist-message.html">人民与强者</a>”的左民人们传达。对于曾担任副总统八年繁荣的候选人来说，这是一个非常奇怪的选择。首先，普通美国人在经济上比以往任何时候都做得更好，为什么他们会心情兴奋地将颠覆性的阶级冲突引入方程式中？似乎是一种“停留”类型的信息，就像乔治·HW Bush在1988年使用的那样，它本来会变得更聪明。其次，如果2000年是推出民粹主义十字军东征的时候，为什么阿尔·戈尔（Al Gore）在过去的八年中没有这样做？无论如何，对于戈尔来说，它似乎并不是很好。</p><p>我认为拜登可能会犯有类似的错误。他对以色列的支持使许多左倾的年轻人对他生气（在<a href="https://twitter.com/micsolana/status/1752718669782642810">Tiktok的一点协助</a>下）。解决这一弱点的一种方法是拥抱一些剩下的年轻人喜欢的事情，例如对气候政策的左派立场。在我看来，这将是一个错误。</p><h4>拜登给了我们更便宜的能量，并在此过程中对气候变化造成了打击</h4><p>大多数左派气候活动家，包括日出运动，灭绝叛乱，格雷塔·敦伯格（Greta Thunberg）等，<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/our-climate-change-debates-are-out">在2010年或更早的世界中仍然非常精神陷入困境</a>。在这个世界观中，只有富裕世界人民的消费减少和惩罚性减少才能避免灾难性的全球灾难。很久以前，这可能是真的，但今天是纯粹的幻想。首先，发达国家作为与中国和亚洲其他地区的全球碳排放量<a href="https://ourworldindata.org/grapher/annual-co2-emissions-per-country?time=1850..latest&amp;country=CHN~USA~OWID_EUR~Asia+%28excl.+China+and+India%29">迅速缩小</a>（不，<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/no-the-us-didnt-outsource-our-carbon">这不是因为外包</a>）。</p><p>但更重要的是，技术的重大变化意味着世界不再面临保持现代生活水平和拯救气候免于灾难的选择。廉价的太阳能和电池每年仍在越来越便宜 -<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/our-climate-change-debates-are-out">完全改变了方程式</a>。我们不再面临丰富和气候稳定之间的选择 - 由于廉价的绿色能源，这些目标现在是一个又一个。</p><p>气候旺克和能量旺克斯意识到了这一事实。企业也是如此；这就是为什么德克萨斯州是一个深红色州，现在已经超过了太阳能的加利福尼亚。 </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3f1a35fa-c8fe-4ef7-8143-71362c131e16_1626x912.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3f1a35fa-c8fe-4ef7-8143-71362c131e16_1626x912.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3f1a35fa-c8fe-4ef7-8143-71362c131e16_1626x912.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3f1a35fa-c8fe-4ef7-8143-71362c131e16_1626x912.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3f1a35fa-c8fe-4ef7-8143-71362c131e16_1626x912.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3f1a35fa-c8fe-4ef7-8143-71362c131e16_1626x912.jpeg" width="1456" height="817" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/3f1a35fa-c8fe-4ef7-8143-71362c131e16_1626x912.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:817,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:64035,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3f1a35fa-c8fe-4ef7-8143-71362c131e16_1626x912.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3f1a35fa-c8fe-4ef7-8143-71362c131e16_1626x912.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3f1a35fa-c8fe-4ef7-8143-71362c131e16_1626x912.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3f1a35fa-c8fe-4ef7-8143-71362c131e16_1626x912.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源：<a href="https://twitter.com/NatBullard/status/1716794734105203000">纳特·布拉德</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>德克萨斯州还可以<a href="https://www.houstonchronicle.com/business/energy/article/ercot-grid-battery-solar-enel-texas-18350609.php">通过电池存储为前进</a>。</p><p>如果太阳能是一种经济效率低下，昂贵的能源形式，那就<em>不会发生</em>这种情况。如果这样做代表经济牺牲或生活水平的降低，德克萨斯人绝不会在庞大的剪辑中建造太阳能。 Ergo，因此，太阳能并不是使我们贫穷的事情。太阳能和电池意味着能源丰度 - 这意味着美国人<em>会消耗更多，而不是更少</em>。他们为自己的房屋获得便宜的电力，从太阳能脱盐的淡化中获得便宜的水，依此类推。</p><p><em>这</em>是我认为拜登需要的气候信息。由于某种原因，他的标志性气候政策被称为“减少通货膨胀法”。这个想法是，太阳能和风能的便宜电力将降低公司的成本，从而降低通货膨胀。爱尔兰共和军可能还没有采取任何措施来降低通货膨胀，但是他们给它起了这个名字的事实表明，民主党人将其视为一种<em>能源丰富的政策</em>。 So a good message is that we&#39;re generating cheaper, more plentiful electricity for Americans, while also fighting climate change in the process.</p><p> In a recent post, <a href="https://www.slowboring.com/p/climate-is-the-problem">Matt Yglesias argued</a> that Biden should focus entirely on a message of cheap energy in general, instead of climate change specifically:</p><blockquote><p> Biden has enacted <em>by far</em> the most consequential climate policies of any president in American history…[But] Biden and the Democrats should triangulate ruthlessly on energy, brag about their successful all-of-the-above [energy] policy, basically never mention climate change, and not enact any new climate-focused policies whatsoever.</p></blockquote><p> I think there&#39;s merit in this suggestion. For example, Biden should absolutely brag about the fact that he helped push US oil production to an all-time high: </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa1b17b85-1c01-4e81-b7b6-d4bb2553ecf7_970x647.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa1b17b85-1c01-4e81-b7b6-d4bb2553ecf7_970x647.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa1b17b85-1c01-4e81-b7b6-d4bb2553ecf7_970x647.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa1b17b85-1c01-4e81-b7b6-d4bb2553ecf7_970x647.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazo